Privacy Policy
Your use of the “WW Scales by Conair UK” application is subject to this Privacy Policy and our
Terms & Conditions
.
We do not collect personally identifiable information about you on the mobile application or website.  Any information that you input into your device is held on your phone only.
Links
This app may contain links to other websites (App store and Google Play). Please be aware that we are not responsible for the privacy practices of other websites. This Privacy Policy applies only to the information on our app. We encourage you to read the privacy policies of other websites you link to from our Website or otherwise visit.
Notification of Changes
We may revise this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we decide to change our Privacy Policy, we will post the revised policy here. As we may make changes at any time without notifying you, we suggest that you periodically consult this Privacy Policy. Please note that our rights to use your personally identifiable information will be based on the Privacy Policy in effect at the time the information is used.
Comments
We have taken great measures to ensure that your visit to our website and mobile application are excellent, and that your privacy is constantly respected. If you have any questions, comments or concerns about our privacy practices, please contact us by email at
